sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Bus as Semantic Event Bus
  participant Graph as Context Graph Projector
  participant Scheduler as Workload Scheduler
  participant Policy as Policy Engine
  participant Assembly as Execution Assembly
  participant Temporal as Temporal Workflow
  participant Runtime as Execution Runtime
  participant Sources as Source Systems
  participant Memory as Memory Engine
  participant Audit as Audit Log

  Bus->>Graph: Deliver semantic event
  Graph->>Graph: Materialize entities, relations, claims
  Graph->>Scheduler: Emit graph delta trigger
  Scheduler->>Policy: Evaluate admission constraints
  Policy-->>Scheduler: Policy decision and required approvals
  Scheduler->>Assembly: Create admitted workload
  Assembly->>Temporal: Start execution graph
  Temporal->>Runtime: Retrieve context
  Temporal->>Runtime: Rank evidence
  Temporal->>Runtime: Execute model or deterministic primitive
  Temporal->>Runtime: Verify claims
  Runtime->>Sources: Validate authoritative facts when required
  Sources-->>Runtime: Source snapshot
  Runtime-->>Temporal: Primitive observations
  Temporal->>Bus: Emit outcome claim events
  Temporal->>Memory: Submit compression candidate
  Memory->>Bus: Emit promoted memory event
  Temporal->>Audit: Record lineage and policy decisions
